{"tid":1320991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同跳橋嗰位弟弟 以及所有行動不便/體能差嘅手足講","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:47:00.000Z","uid":191633,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f77b3b52fe5b0c5b9cdea55b99c35689de71f0c","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"第一件事，發任何夢時，千奇千奇，唔好單丁一個！雖然講咗好多次口都臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你真係自己一個去現場嘅話，請你拍一拍你身邊任何人，同佢地down聲自己係單丁，問下可唔可以join佢地。我相信呢度任何一個人都願意同你一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請你相信我地可以照顧你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二件事，如果一旦要撤離夢境，請你務必同身邊任何人講自己行動不便，尋求協助。有發過夢嘅人都知道，夢入面嘅人都好互助互愛，一定會用任何方法帶你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，我想同在座各位講，除咗提防惡犬，記得要睇實身邊有無疑似單丁嘅人，必要時問下佢地有無需要幫手。香港嘅細路係我地嘅未來，係用嚟錫，唔係用嚟做犧牲品！請好好愛護所有學生同年輕人，以及好好保護所有有心出嚟護港嘅人，唔好俾佢地受傷/受驚/被捕！"},{"pid":"4992af9b17fc53c63ad5f0e916bbdb526e88325e","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c65812f78c8b6692f6d7c5ff491d25dd1bfe5394","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9b9b4c1c79dbee12165c48092a5cc0803bbf5ba7","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3a199a68d071495399347df251f596b6a4220103","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d3f69855c790eb46b5160c98668087ecf4625334","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb51fc5ff0c265f11d60f3d8901bc9a21b40e247","tid":1320991,"uid":260354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"真係 唔洗怕羞 出得黎都係同路人"},{"pid":"db3c6ced7ad80e92de69593dae78b76505999d3a","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"今日大家要照顧好陳伯！"},{"pid":"0a71a4b2e3cfca7c68c68a96787db4ce6077be59","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:12:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"582b9b634acf7b2118404238bdbd9a151f9d3ad5","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec4f2de8ad6172c3aca8885d4963e96b5fc228c5","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"082fc414483b8524718de99424236d6fee848c43","tid":1320991,"uid":261043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"167f804912def2987cdead53a6f479ce41098deb","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d110ededcd863d4f08c4f616069dc8450b5d038f","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"大家要避免小朋友被狗咬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701a47beef6abd0185192f1e9201e711e055ee40","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a69719515e2d5174b9b5d9a753314c719653797","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd58dc28de875952fe2f60b0d7a5aa54013e19a","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e6325670828b9023cc05aaf8ce80a3ebbe3ba52","tid":1320991,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score